gomodel:SYNGO_5383  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 2k: immunogold EM of mouse DRG neurons showed chemokine-like secreted protein TAFA4 localized at the membranes of synaptic vesicles, in a presynaptic terminal where some vesicles were stained for VGLUT3.. Experimental description: mice were used for all experiments. \"Sixteen TAFA4Venus heterozygous (±) knock in mice\", \"Twelve 3-week-old GINIP mice\", Six CD1 mice (n = 3 for LM; n = 3 for EM), as control animals to verify peptidergic and non-peptidergic marker expression in genetically unmodified animals." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" ;
        dc:date           "2023-03-14" ;
